description:
If you see anything posted about the GC Session, it's done by the GC Communication Department. They are the ones to put up the posts, launch the videos, and manage the social media coverage. In this episode of ANN Late Nite(ish), Kenia pop's into Jennifer Stymiest's office in the GC Communication Department who shares all the ways that they will be broadcasting Session to the world.

#GCSession #ANN #AdventistChurch #Adventist
